JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Salespeople
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ar_salesperson_territory

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Warehouses
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: IC_WAREHOUSE_CDS

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Detail
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
il.invoice_num as invoice_num,line_num,0 as release_num,il.doc_num as doc_num,amt_ordered,amt_shipped,price,item_num,
{fn rtrim(description_1)} + ' ' + description_2 as Description,um_selling,ship_date,il.init_whse as init_whse,amt_shipped * price as LineTotal
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_past_inv_line il inner join so_past_inv_head ih on ih.company = il.company and ih.invoice_num = il.invoice_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
ih.invoice_num as invoice_num,inv_cm_date,customer_num,ship_to,po_num,doc_type,merchandise_amt,misc_amt,freight,tax,invoice_disc,merchandise_amt + misc_amt + freight + tax - invoice_disc as InvoiceTotal,
reference_num,terms_code,tax_code,ship_ref_date,slsp_terr,
customer_name,customer_addr_1,customer_addr_2,customer_city,customer_state_code,customer_zip_code,
customer_country,name,address_1,address_2,city,state_code,zip_code,country,0 as IsOpen
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_past_inv_addr ia  join so_past_inv_head ih on ia.company = ih.company and ia.doc_num = ih.doc_num and ia.invoice_num = ih.invoice_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer Product
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj SO_REM_CUST_ITEM ci inner join IC_INVENTRY_MAST i on i.company = ci.company and i.item_num = ci.erp_item_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Product
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
item_num,{fn RTRIM(description_1)} + ' ' + description_2 as Description,item_class,um_selling, taxable,item_price_cls,
list_price, stocked, model_number, primary_vnd_num,vendor_item_num
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ic_inventry_mast

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Vendor
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj ap_vendor_mast v join ic_inventry_mast i on i.company = v.company and i.primary_vnd_num = v.vendor_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Alternate Units of Measure
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: { oj ic_um_by_item ium inner join ic_inventry_mast im on ium.company = im.company and ium.item_num = im.item_num }
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: im.company = '{IntegrationConnector_FactsCompanyNumber}' and ium.ok_selling = 'Y' and im.allow_web_purchase = 'Y' and im.active = 'Y'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer BillTo=ShipTo
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ar_cust_mast

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: ShipTos
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ar_ship_to_addr

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: customer_num,'' as customer_seq, customer_name,address_1,address_2,address_3,city, state_code,zip_code,country,phone_1,contact_1,email_1,normal_ship_to, customer_class,slsp_terr,  tax_code,terms_code,credit_limit,on_hold,default_branch,active, {fn REPLACE(po_required,'A','Y')} AS 'po_required',cust_price_class,ship_via,ecomm_whse
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ar_cust_mast

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Open Orders - Temp Addresses
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_sales_order_headers oh inner join ar_ship_to_addr st on st.company = oh.company and st.customer_num = oh.cust_num and st.ship_to = oh.doc_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice History Detail
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
il.doc_num as order_num,line_num,0 as release_num,amt_ordered ,amt_total_ship,price,item_num,
{fn rtrim(description_1)} + ' ' + description_2 as Description,um_selling,ship_date,il.init_whse as init_whse, amt_ordered * price as LineTotal,ship_date,ih.customer_num as customer_num,ship_to
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_past_inv_line il inner join so_past_inv_head ih on ih.company = il.company and ih.doc_num = il.doc_num}
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
il.company = '{IntegrationConnector_FactsCompanyNumber}'
and
{fn timestampdiff(sql_tsi_day,inv_cm_date, {fn CURDATE()})} < 10 and doc_type = 'I'
order by il.doc_num,il.invoice_num,il.line_num

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice History Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
ih.doc_num as order_num,order_date,customer_num,ship_to,po_num,merchandise_amt + misc_amt + freight + tax - invoice_disc as OrderTotal,merchandise_amt,misc_amt,freight,tax,invoice_disc,
reference_num,terms_code,tax_code,ship_ref_date,slsp_terr,
customer_name,customer_addr_1,customer_addr_2,customer_city,customer_state_code,customer_zip_code,
customer_country,name,address_1,address_2,city,state_code,zip_code,country,0 as ZeroAmount
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_past_inv_addr ia join so_past_inv_head ih on ia.company = ih.company and ia.doc_num = ih.doc_num and ia.invoice_num = ih.invoice_num}
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
ih.company = '{IntegrationConnector_FactsCompanyNumber}' and doc_type = 'I' and
{fn timestampdiff(sql_tsi_day,inv_cm_date, {fn CURDATE()})} < 10

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Open Order History - Billing Address
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: so_sales_order_soldto_address

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Open Order Header - Base
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: cust_num,ship_to_num,doc_num,order_date,po_num,status_code,soh.ship_via as ship_via,ordered_by,ship_date,merchandise_amt,misc_amt,tax,freight_amt,reference_num,init_whse,salesperson_terr,soh.terms_code as terms_code,soh.tax_code as tax_code,merchandise_amt+misc_amt+tax+Freight_amt as OrderTotal,customer_name, address_1,address_2,city,state_code,zip_code,country,0 as ZeroAmount
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_sales_order_headers soh left outer join ar_cust_mast cm on soh.company = cm.company and soh.cust_num = cm.customer_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Open Order Header - Standard Ship-To <> Bill-To
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj so_sales_order_headers oh inner join ar_ship_to_addr st on st.company = oh.company and st.customer_num = oh.cust_num and st.ship_to = oh.ship_to_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Open Order Lines
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
sol.doc_num as order_num,line_num,0 as release_num,cust_num,ship_to_num,amount_ordered,amount_shipped,amount_backordered,line_item_status,price,ship_whse,sol.po_num,amount_ordered * price as LineTotal,
item_num,{fn rtrim(description_1)} + ' ' + description_2 as description,um_selling
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
{oj SO_SALES_ORDER_LINE_ITEMS sol join SO_SALES_ORDER_HEADERS soh on soh.company = sol.company
and soh.doc_num = sol.doc_num}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Alternate Products
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj (ic_substitute_items si inner join ic_inventry_mast i1 on i1.company = si.company and i1.item_num = si.item_num) inner join ic_inventry_mast i2 on i2.company = si.company and i2.item_num = si.sub_item}
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: si.company = '{IntegrationConnector_FactsCompanyNumber}' and i1.active = 'Y' and i1.allow_web_purchase = 'Y' and i2.active = 'Y' and i2.allow_web_purchase = 'Y'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Companion Products
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: {oj (so_companion_lines cl inner join ic_inventry_mast i1 on i1.company = cl.company and i1.item_num = cl.pitem) inner join ic_inventry_mast i2 on i2.company = cl.company and i2.item_num = cl.citem}
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cl.company = '{IntegrationConnector_FactsCompanyNumber}' and cl.citem <> 'M' and i1.active = 'Y' and i1.allow_web_purchase = 'Y' and i2.active = 'Y' and i2.allow_web_purchase = 'Y'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Carriers
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: so_ship_via_file

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Ship Via
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: so_ship_via_file

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Payment Methods
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ar_terms_codes

Name: FACTSxx: Inventory Refresh
Description: FACTS Inventory refresh if you do not use real-time inventory calls

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Inventory
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
{oj ic_warehouse_itm iw inner join ic_inventry_mast im on im.company = iw.company and 
im.item_num = iw.item_num}
